<exercise checkit-seed="0016" checkit-slug="M4" checkit-title="Finding a matrix inverse">
  <statement>
    <p>Show how to find the inverse of the matrix <m>Q= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
2 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 &amp; 3 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; -1 &amp; 8 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 3 \\
1 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 &amp; -2
\end{array}\right] </m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>Q^{-1}= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
6 &amp; -5 &amp; 0 &amp; -11 \\
3 &amp; -3 &amp; 1 &amp; -6 \\
-5 &amp; 4 &amp; 1 &amp; 10 \\
-1 &amp; 1 &amp; 0 &amp; 2
\end{array}\right] </me>
  </answer>
</exercise>

